free-your-disk (0.1.0) unstable; urgency=low

  * Initial release.
  * Disk scanning and safe cleanup: temporary files, largest files, git
    worktrees and developer caches.
  * Recoverable-by-default deletion (XDG trash), dry-run preview, Polkit
    helper for privileged cleanup.
  * System tray icon with a disk-usage popover widget.

